getHeader

Header getHeader(String headerName)
Get the value of an individual Header. If there are multiple values for the same header, this method will return the first one found. If you expect there to be multiple values for the same header then you should use getHeaders(String).

Parameters:
headerName - The name of the header
Returns:
The Header associated with that name. Possibly null.
